body_html: Just got told my #4476 is a duplicate of this ticket, so coming here with: Is there anything I can do to get this fixed up? It seems to be hitting a number of external contributors and it's been 10 days since it was first reported. A time suck for all of us to be rediscovering it and working out the same patches!
